  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This investigation is designed to demonstrate the clinical efficacy and safety of the
      low-dose drug of the SIELLO leads in comparison to the non-steroid BPPU leads in a clinical
      investigation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
